title: Uncommon Knowledge Full Discography [LAME Encoded 245 Kbps VBR M
description:

This torrent includes all three albums:

-The Storm
-Rainy Day
-Operation: Rolling Thunder

As said in the title, encoded by LAME, 245 Kbps VBR.

Scans of all album art, inner cover, and back. Some inner covers are autographed, and have large blank spaces where the special thanks should be. I only erased the special thanks area to protect the identity of those neither in the band, or guests of the band.
